---
import Layout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Autional — Identity for AI-Generated Applications" description="Open-source identity infrastructure. Authentication, accounts, multi-tenancy, and access control. Build with AI, ship with confidence.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-tight">Your AI App Needs Users.<br/> <span class="text-primary-600">We've Got That.</span></h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">The identity layer for AI-generated applications. Autional gives your AI-born app a complete user system — authentication, accounts, multi-tenancy, and access control. Built on 24 open-source microservices. Integrate in minutes, not sprints.</p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/docs" class="rounded-lg bg-primary-600 px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-primary-700 shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/25">Get Started</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/autional/authms" class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700 px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 border-t border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      <div><div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">24</div><div class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-1">Microservices</div></div>
      <div><div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">1,400+</div><div class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-1">API Endpoints</div></div>
      <div><div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">AGPL</div><div class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-1">Open Source</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 border-t border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
    <div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">How It Works</h2></div>
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3 text-center">
      <div class="p-8"><div class="inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary-50 text-primary-600 text-lg font-bold">1</div><h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold">Integrate</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">Add Autional to your stack via API or SDK. Auto-generated TypeScript types from OpenAPI specs. Works with any language or framework.</p></div>
      <div class="p-8"><div class="inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary-50 text-primary-600 text-lg font-bold">2</div><h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold">Configure</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">Define auth flows, enable MFA, configure SSO, set up multi-tenancy. All via API or admin console. Every feature is optional.</p></div>
      <div class="p-8"><div class="inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary-50 text-primary-600 text-lg font-bold">3</div><h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold">Ship</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">From MVP to enterprise without migration. Start with email/password, add enterprise SSO when your customers need it. Same codebase, zero rewrites.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Grid -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 border-t border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
    <div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Enterprise Identity,<br/>Open Source</h2><p class="mt-4 text-neutral-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">24 microservices, 1,400+ APIs, and enterprise compliance features — all open source under AGPL.</p></div>
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      {[['🔐','Authentication','Email/password, social login, magic link, passkey. Complete user registration and login system.'],
        ['🛡️','MFA & Passkey','TOTP, SMS, email OTP, WebAuthn/FIDO2, adaptive MFA. Enterprise-grade security.'],
        ['🏢','Enterprise SSO','SAML 2.0, OIDC, OAuth 2.0, LDAP/AD. Self-service IdP configuration.'],
        ['👥','Multi-Tenancy','Per-tenant data isolation, custom domains, white-label. Built for B2B SaaS.'],
        ['📊','Audit & Compliance','Hash-chain audit logs, GDPR DSAR automation, SOX/ISO27001 mapping.'],
        ['⚡','Developer API','1,400+ REST endpoints, gRPC, webhooks. Auto-generated TypeScript SDKs.'],
      ].map(([icon,title,desc]) => (
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">{icon}</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">{title}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-primary-600 px-8 py-16 text-center text-white">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">AI Generates Apps. We Generate Users.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-primary-100 max-w-xl mx-auto">24 microservices. 1,400+ APIs. AGPL open source.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://github.com/autional/authms" class="rounded-lg bg-white px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-50">GitHub</a>
        <a href="/docs" class="rounded-lg border border-primary-400 px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-primary-500">Documentation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
